<!-- Start Body -->
During last year, I tried smoking 2C-B. The first couple of times I added it to some weed in a pipe and the effects were fairly nice, but not as strong as ingesting it. After some experimentation I found that if I put 5mg in the end of a glass tube and used a torch get it real hot, then inhaled it and held it in for a real long time, I would get an unbelieveable rush and a righteous 2C-B trip that lasted about 4 hours instead of the usual 6-9. Some of my friends tried it too and liked it a lot, but we never felt like we needed to do it again right away because the effects were so strong and satisfying. I suspected that smoking 2C-B was quite bad for the lungs so I stopped smoking it after a while. Also, the intensity of the experience got to be a bit much after a while. The first rush can be very powerful.<!-- End Body -->
<br/><br style="clear:both;"/>


